'========================

On Error GoTo ErrorHandles
    
    
    Call SP_CRTxLogMallCardExtend(("Date:" & Date & " Time:" & Time$ & " Msg: " & "SP_PRCxPointALL (1) Start")) '*Thirapong 64-12-28 เพิ่ม Log Monitor ไว้ตรวจสอบปัญหา CommSheet TTK-ISS3000-796 TK-ISSUE - Missing BP award to TKPlat.xlsx

    If Not SP_CHKbEmpAlowPoint Then             '*Ao 2013/07/31 CommSheet TK-ISS3000-196-ST 00 00 02.xls
